-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- vw_omics_modalities: Registry of omics assay modalities: RNA-seq, ATAC-seq, proteomics, metabolomics, methylomes, chromatin-conformation, immune-receptor repertoires, microbiomes, and long-read genomes.
